videos.description: Shaquille Morris dunks the lob from Landry Shamet for the Shockers.
videos.headline: Wichita State's Morris slams home alley-oop

videos.description: Austin Dasent swishes a 3-pointer to give the Tigers a 15-12 lead in the first half against Wichita State.
videos.headline: Savannah State's Dasent hits 3 for the lead

videos.description: Samajae Haynes-Jones goes coast-to-coast and finishes with a Euro-step layup.
videos.headline: Wichita State's Jones steal and Euro-step layup

videos.description: Landry Shamet hits a 3-pointer off to increase the Shockers lead to 49-27 in the first half.
videos.headline: Wichita State's ball movement results in Shamet 3

videos.description: Darral Willis scores on reverse layup while getting fouled for the Shockers in the second half.
videos.headline: Wichita State's Willis scores on reverse layup and-1

videos.description: Kaelan Malone's over-the-head pass to Rashard Kelly for a slam dunk in transition increases the Shockers' lead.
videos.headline: Malone throws over-the-head pass to Kelly for dunk

videos.description: Samajae Haynes-Jones scores a left-handed layup to give the Shockers its largest lead of the game.
videos.headline: Haynes-Jones with fast break layup

videos.description: Rashard Kelly throws down a thunderous right-handed dunk in transition for the Wichita State.
videos.headline: Kelly rumbles and slams home the dunk

videos.description: With Brycen Bush's 3-pointer, the Shockers set a school record with 66 bench points in the game.
videos.headline: Wichita State's Bush hits 3 and sets school record
